 for other developing countries.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aEducationxCas, Études dexPays en voie de développement. 0aEducationxCase studiesxDeveloping countries. 0aEducationxGuyana. 0aEducationzDeveloping countriesvCase studies. 0aEducationzGuyana. 0aÉducationxCas, Études dexPays en voie de développement. 0aÉducationxGuyana. 4aEducation. 4aSocial Science: Development Studies. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Developing & Emerging Countries.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010z978311127416408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010z978311127724040uhttps://doi.org/10.51644/978088920890240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780889208902423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780889208902/original  a978-3-11-127416-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010b2010  a978-3-11-127724-0  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010b2010  aGBV-deGruyter-alles